glowstick
    by mojombo http://github.com/mojombo/glowstick

== FEATURES/PROBLEMS:
  
  Can draw a line. In a window!
  It does not yet glow.

== SYNOPSIS:

  Simple line graph using OpenGL. In a window!

== REQUIREMENTS:

  You need the ruby-opengl gem. You may need some libs to get that working.
  If so, these would be them: libgl1-mesa-dev libglu1-mesa-dev libglut3-dev

== INSTALL:

  Clone the repo
 
== SAMPLE

  cd /path/to/repo
  irb

  $:.unshift(File.join('.', 'lib'))
  require 'lib/glowstick'
  Glowstick::VERSION
  graph = Glowstick::Graph.new
  graph.data = 12, 14, 17, 16, 11
  glow = Glowstick.new(nil)
  glow.start
  # Press "ESC" to exit

